Hyundai Motor America, aunit of Hyundai Motor Co of South Korea, said domestic carsales during the month of March rose to 19,502 compared witrh10,432 during March last year.    Year-to-date car sales rose to 56,164 from 11,020 duringthe same period last year, the company said.    Hyundai began selling cars in the United States lastFebruary 20. Reuter&#3;